```systemverilog
module mult_dsp #(
parameter WIDTH = 16
)(
input  wire signed [WIDTH-1:0] a,
input  wire signed [WIDTH-1:0] b,
output wire signed [2*WIDTH-1:0] p
);
// 关键：两个操作数都是变量，且未加任何移位限制
